Description: Naruto meets a former classmate and must face-off with him... to the death!
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 52
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife. In this volume, a look at how "soul catching" was done 100 years ago.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 36
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: Misao Harada can see into a magical realm where she is the bride demon of prophecy. In the volume, the truth about a past incident is revealed, but is it worth the pain it will cause?
Title: BLACK BIRD, VOL. 10
Author: Kanoko Sakurakoji

Description: After the death of her brother, Teru Kurebayashi has been receiving comforting messages from Daisy, who communicates through her brotherâ€™s cell phone. In this installment, Teru gets kidnapped.
Title: DENGEKI DAISY, VOL. 6
Author: Kyousuke Motomi

Description: Ah, high school: Sawako has a crush on Kazehaya, but when a new popular guy shows interest in her, will Sawako and Kazehaya be pulled apart?
Title: KIMI NI TODOKE: FROM ME TO YOU, VOL. 10
Author: Karuho Shiina

Description: In a distant future, the government decides to ban books and the libraries have formed their own group to defend their collections. In this volume, a romantic triangle begins to form.
Title: LIBRARY WARS: LOVE & WAR, VOL. 6
Author: Hiro Arikawa

Description: Rin Okumura joins an exorcist academy in order to control his inner demon. Will his classmates find out about his satanic bloodline?
Title: BLUE EXORCIST, VOL. 1
Author: Kazue Kato

Description: This is an upstairs/downstairs drama and romance between Choko Kuze and her current boss (and former servant) Masayuki Domoto. The series concludes with this volume.
Title: BUTTERFLIES, FLOWERS, VOL. 8
Author: Yuki Yoshihara

Description: Ultimo and Vice are the embodiment of good and evil. In this installment, meet Jealousy and Rune!
Title: ULTIMO, VOL. 6
Author: Hiroyuki Takei

Description: Light Yagami discovers a supernatural notebook that allows him to murder anyone he has seen by writing their name in it. He uses this ability to try to rid the world of evil.
Title: DEATH NOTE BLACK EDITION, VOL. 5
Author: Tsugumi Ohba
